I assume you are asking us to update our binaries uploaded to pypi.
We will update those once we verify that rc(release candidate) versions are sufficiently stable.
Until then, please Use the URLs here to download our pre-built binaries for different operating systems:
https://www.tensorflow.org/versions/r1.0/get_started/os_setup#pip_installation
